{
  "id": "L09",
  "title": "Buying Clothes",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Welcome! In this lesson, you'll learn how to ask for help in a French clothing store, 'un magasin de vêtements'."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V01",
      "data": {
        "un magasin de vêtements": "a clothing store"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Excusez-moi",
        "meaning": "Excuse me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonjour",
        "meaning": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je cherche...",
        "meaning": "I am looking for..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V02",
      "data": {
        "un pull": "a sweater"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V03",
      "data": {
        "bleu": "blue"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In French, colors like 'bleu' (blue) usually come *after* the noun. For example: 'un pull bleu'."
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L09_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "cherche",
        "phonetic": "[ʃɛʁʃ]",
        "tip": "The 'ch' sound in French is soft, like 'sh' in the English word 'shoe'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Quelle est votre taille ?",
        "meaning": "What is your size?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je fais du...",
        "meaning": "I wear size..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Voilà",
        "meaning": "Here you go"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L09_S01",
      "title": "Asking for Assistance",
      "setting": "You're in a clothing store and see a shop assistant. Get their attention and ask for what you want.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Get the assistant's attention",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Say you're looking for a blue sweater",
          "chatbot_message": "Bonjour !",
          "extract_info": {
            "item": "The item and color the user is looking for"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "State your size",
          "chatbot_message": "D'accord, un {item}. Quelle est votre taille ?",
          "extract_info": {
            "user_size": "The user's clothing size"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge the assistant",
          "chatbot_message": "La taille {user_size}. Voilà."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Great! Now that you have the item, let's find the fitting rooms to try it on."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Où sont...?",
        "meaning": "Where are...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V04",
      "data": {
        "les cabines d'essayage": "the fitting rooms"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L09_P02",
      "data": {
        "word": "essayage",
        "phonetic": "[e.sɛ.jaʒ]",
        "tip": "The 'ge' at the end sounds like the 's' in the English word 'measure'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "C'est...",
        "meaning": "It is..."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V05",
      "data": {
        "trop grand": "too big"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V06",
      "data": {
        "trop petit": "too small"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Vous avez en...?",
        "meaning": "Do you have it in...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L09_S02",
      "title": "Trying on Clothes",
      "setting": "The assistant gave you the sweater. Now, find the fitting rooms and check the size.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Ask where the fitting rooms are",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Say the sweater is too big",
          "chatbot_message": "Les cabines d'essayage sont là-bas.",
          "extract_info": {
            "fit_issue": "The fit problem, e.g. 'trop grand' or 'trop petit'"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask for the item in a smaller size",
          "chatbot_message": "Ah, c'est {fit_issue}. D'accord.",
          "extract_info": {
            "new_size": "The new size requested"
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Acknowledge receiving the new item",
          "chatbot_message": "Oui. Voilà en taille {new_size}."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "The new size fits! Let's tell the assistant you'll buy it and find the checkout."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V07",
      "data": {
        "parfait": "perfect"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je le prends",
        "meaning": "I'll take it"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "The word 'le' in 'Je le prends' means 'it'. It refers to a masculine noun, like 'un pull'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Où est...?",
        "meaning": "Where is...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V08",
      "data": {
        "la caisse": "the checkout"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L09_P03",
      "data": {
        "word": "caisse",
        "phonetic": "[kɛs]",
        "tip": "The 'ai' sound here is short, like the 'e' in the English word 'bed'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Je peux...?",
        "meaning": "Can I...?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V09",
      "data": {
        "échanger": "to exchange"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V10",
      "data": {
        "oui": "yes"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L09_V11",
      "data": {
        "le ticket de caisse": "the receipt"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Merci",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L09_E14",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Bonne journée",
        "meaning": "Have a good day"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L09_S03",
      "title": "Deciding and Paying",
      "setting": "The new sweater is a perfect fit. Now it's time to buy it and leave the store.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Say the new size is perfect and you'll buy it",
          "chatbot_message": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask where the checkout is",
          "chatbot_message": "Parfait !"
        },
        {
          "title": "Ask if you can exchange the item",
          "chatbot_message": "La caisse est là-bas."
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank the cashier",
          "chatbot_message": "Oui, avec le ticket de caisse."
        },
        {
          "title": "Say goodbye",
          "chatbot_message": "Bonne journée !"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}